##: # bltriangle
##:
##: Arguments: freq, amp
##:
##: **bltriangle** is a band-limited triangle wave generator. For paramters, 
##: it takes in a frequency, and an amplitude.
##:
##: **bltriangle** has two other aliases: **tri**, and **triangle**.
##:
##: The argument below creates a simple 440hz triangle sound.
##---
440 0.3 bltriangle
##---
